en.description: The Itzal is a stealth and support Archwing utilizing technologies that can hide it from enemy attention while it attacks with powerful disruptive abilities, sacrificing durability for a high amount of energy capacity.
en.codex: Designed for quick clandestine attacks, the Itzal Archwing excels at striking from the darkness of space.

ru.description: Спроектированные для быстрых и скрытых атак, Арчвинг Итзал идеален для ударов из тьмы космоса.
